  <h2>1. Who we are</h2>
  <p>Tessera is operated by <strong>Veridion Studios Ltd.</strong> ("Veridion," "we," "us," or "our"). We provide a marketplace platform that connects clients with vetted software developers, with integrated escrow-protected payments powered by Stripe.</p>

  <h2>2. Eligibility</h2>
  <p>You must be at least 18 years old and legally capable of entering into binding contracts. By using Tessera, you represent that you meet these requirements. We reserve the right to verify your identity at any time.</p>

  <h2>3. Account registration</h2>
  <p>You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your login credentials and for all activity that occurs under your account. You must provide accurate, current, and complete information during registration and keep it up to date.</p>
